''See also [[Hotel]], [[hôtel]]''
==English==

===Pronunciation===
*[[IPA]]: /həʊˈtɛl/, /əʊˈtɛl/
*[[SAMPA]]: /h@U"tEl/, /@U"tEl/
''The pronunciation omitting the initial h is in imitation of the French'' '''[[hôtel]]''' ''and is now old-fashioned''

===Noun===
'''hotel''' (''plural:'' '''[[hotels]]''')

# An [[establishment]] that provides [[accommodation]] and other services for paying guests; normally larger than a [[guest house]], and often one of a [[chain]].
# The letter ''H'' in the [[ICAO spelling alphabet]].

